Package com.GREENWORKS.eco.data

Class DatabaseCleaner

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.GREENWORKS.eco.data.DatabaseCleaner
  • public class DatabaseCleaner
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will remove redundant points from the locations table and put them in the problem_locations table. The class has the ability to determine which redundant points are good, so the good points will remain in the locations table.

      • findProblems

        public java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,​java.util.ArrayList<Pin>> findProblems​(java.util.List<Pin> pinList)
        This method goes through the pinList that is provided to it and isolates Pins that have the same address. It also adds pins that have addresses earlier than the present day to an ArrayList that holds pins with old dates.
        Parameters:
        pinList - The List that will be analyzed.

      • solveConflicts

        public java.util.ArrayList<Pin> solveConflicts​(java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,​java.util.ArrayList<Pin>> addressPinMap)
        This method solves the conflicted pin address by removing pins that have typical markers for invalid data entries. If a new marker is identified this is where it should be added.
        Parameters:

        Returns:
        Returns the solution ArrayList.
